      <description>This Career Clip features Lucinda Lawson, Director of Human Resources with Coordinated Health, Bethlehem, PA.  Every young person should begin to question every adult that they interact with and ask for details about their careers and if they are happy.  They should be sure to ask if they are happy, what education they needed to get where they are, how much money do they make, etc.  Adults around students should be open and share with the kids  the information that will help this young person determine a career.</description>
